1. Momak* je otišao u prodavnicu. (The guy* went to the store.)
2. Vidjela sam momka u parku. (I saw a guy* in the park.)
3. On je pravi momak*. (He is a real guy*.)
4. Momak* je bio ljut. (The guy* was angry.)
5. Sinoć sam upoznala zgodnog momka*. (Last night I met a handsome guy*.)
6. Oni su momci* iz komšiluka. (They are guys* from the neighborhood.)
7. Momak* je trčao ulicom. (The guy* was running down the street.)
8. On je bio momčina* u školi. (He was a big guy* in school.)
9. Ovaj momak* mi se sviđa. (I like this guy*.)
10. Pridružio sam se momcima* na zabavi. (I joined the guys* at the party.)